  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "A Nintendo DS game released as part of the Kuroshitsuji universe.\nThe story is original and takes place between Chapter 13 and Chapter 14. The basic plot is that the Phantomhives are sent to the haunted Brighton mansion by Queen Victoria because of the recent sightings of ghosts on the property, which she would like him to resolve. Manga creator Yana Toboso oversaw the story and created new characters for the game.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The ghost is here to stay.\n\nThe player controls either Ciel Phantomhive or Sebastian Michaelis in a choose-your-own adventure-esque game, where players can choose from various dialogue options throughout the game. It is the player's job to solve puzzles and mini-games in the adventure mode to gain special items.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
